body:
Select LIO.Tarih,OVI.VeriIslemAdi,LIO.InfoParams,LIO.InfoKayit From
  IT15_LogsITObjects LIO
LEFT OUTER JOIN  IT15_ObjectsVeriIslemleri OVI On OVI.ITVeriIslemID = LIO.ITVeriIslemID
LEFT OUTER JOIN  IT15_ObjectsM OM On OM.ITObjectID = LIO.DSITobjectID
LEFT OUTER JOIN IT15_ObjectsM OMSP On OMSP.ITObjectID = OVI.SPITObjectID
Where LIO.InfoID Like '%(PlanMakinaID:14154$CURSOR$%' Order By LIO.ITObjectsLogID Desc
